    "extras": [
      "For a train-heavy version, Rajdhani or other AC overnight trains can replace the Jaipur–Varanasi or Delhi–Mumbai flight legs, but they take a full night and need early IRCTC booking.",
      "ASI monuments generally offer slightly cheaper cashless tickets online, so pre-book Red Fort, Humayun's Tomb, Qutub Minar, Taj Mahal and Agra Fort whenever your dates are fixed.",
      "Start monument days at sunrise in Delhi, Agra and Jaipur; lines and haze build quickly after 10 AM in peak season.",
      "UPI works widely in cities, but keep ₹2,000–₹4,000 in cash for rickshaws, station porters, smaller ghatside cafés and beach shacks."
    ],
